OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,C'unprepared' for scale of disorder
OL,6,FA report by His Majesty's Inspectorate
OL,7,Fof Constabulary and Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FServices (HMICFRS), released on
OL,9,FWednesday, examines how police
OL,10,Fresponded to riots sparked by the
OL,11,Fmurder of three girls in Southport.
OL,13,FBebe King, six, Alice Da Silva Aguiar,
OL,14,Fnine, and Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven,
OL,15,Fdied after stabbings at a Taylor Swift-
OL,16,Fthemed dance class on July 29. Axel
OL,17,FRudakubana, 18, who is accused of
OL,18,Ftheir murder is due to appear in court
OL,19,Fon Wednesday.
