OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,C'unprepared' for scale of disorder
OL,6,FSoon after their deaths, more than 600
OL,7,Fpeople were arrested as police cracked
OL,8,Fdown on what Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer called "far-right thuggery,"
OL,10,Fwith crowds targeting mosques and
OL,11,Fasylum seeker accommodation.
OL,13,FThe report found that many events in
OL,14,F2023 and 2024, involving an "extreme
OL,15,Fnationalist sentiment," were signs of
OL,16,Fpotential future disorder, but this
OL,17,Fwas not reflected in police
OL,18,Fintelligence assessments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
