OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,C'unprepared' for scale of disorder
OL,6,FThe report said: "We have found that
OL,7,Fthe series of incidents of violence
OL,8,Fand disorder across the UK during 2023
OL,9,Fand 2024 should have influenced the
OL,10,Fpolice service's assessments of threat
OL,11,Fand risk.
OL,13,F"Our assessment of these incidents
OL,14,Fsuggests that the risks of disorder
OL,15,Fwere greater than the police believed
OL,16,Fthem to be. They involved extreme
OL,17,Fnationalist sentiment, aggravated
OL,18,Factivism or serious disorder.
