OL,3,CSouthport riots review finds police
OL,4,C'unprepared' for scale of disorder
OL,6,FChief Inspector of Constabulary Andy
OL,7,FCooke said: "We found the police
OL,8,Fdecisions to co-ordinate and mobilise
OL,9,Fthose public order officers nationally
OL,10,Fwere made too late, and the police
OL,11,Fdidn't have a proper intelligence
OL,12,Fpicture of the rising tide of violence.
OL,14,F"There were gaps in their intelligence
OL,15,Ffunctions, especially around the
OL,16,Fanalysis of social media and other
OL,17,Fdark web media, and no one understood
OL,18,For could counter the emerging cause
OL,19,Fand effect of that misinformation and
OL,20,Fdisinformation.
