OL,6,FMr Cooke has called for a national co-
OL,7,Fordinator to instruct forces to
OL,8,Fprovide mutual aid and argued some
OL,9,Fchief constables had dragged their
OL,10,Ffeet over doing so.
OL,12,FHe added that he was concerned about
OL,13,Fsome officers being sent out in
OL,14,Fregular uniform rather than riot gear.
OL,16,FMr Cooke said: "I doubt it will be
OL,17,Fanother 14 years before we see serious
OL,18,Fdisorder. I hope it is, but I doubt it.
