OL,6,FThe report said: "We acknowledge that
OL,7,Fuse of water cannon by police in Great
OL,8,FBritain would be highly controversial.
OL,10,F"There is limited police or other
OL,11,Facademic evidence about the
OL,12,Feffectiveness of its use. Opinions
OL,13,Fremain divided, even among senior
OL,14,Fpolice officers.
OL,16,F"And it was beyond the scope of this
OL,17,Freview to evaluate water cannon as a
OL,18,Fpotential tactical option."
